      "text": "今日の大会、絶対に勝ってみせます\n志半ばで倒れちゃった芽衣ちゃんのためにも……！",
      "startTime": 11.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の場合、単にお腹壊しちゃっただけなんだが……\nさくらがやる気十分なら、もう何も言うまい",
      "startTime": 20.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
