      "text": "えへへ！　トロフィーとCM撮影のお仕事は\n私がしっかりゲットしてきちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 27.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
