      "text": "わぁ、おっきなスイーツが沢山！\nクマさんさくらがぜーんぶ食べちゃうぞ",
      "startTime": 89.7666697186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "大食いは得意なんだからっ\nあおぉ～ん！！",
      "startTime": 96.9666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
