      "text": "じゃあ、こっちでいきましょう！\nがおぉ～！！　クマさんさくらだぞ～！",
      "startTime": 112.266673279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ここにあるスイーツ、全部私のだ～！　えへへ",
      "startTime": 118.4333508811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
