      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "これできっと、大会に出たかったはずの芽衣ちゃんも\n報われましたよね……ぐすっ",
      "startTime": 159.8666636152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣のことがどんどん大袈裟になっていくな……）",
      "startTime": 164.1000038149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
