      "text": "でも、大食いで勝てたのは嬉しかったですけど……",
      "startTime": 167.7333371482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_10_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりスイーツは、せっかくならじっくり\n味わって食べたかったかも……なんて",
      "startTime": 175.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
